user.biography:
Blend, but don’t blend in. 🎨💞
✉️ business@spinandco.com

node.text: when I was back home a few weeks ago, I surprised some of the students at Arbor Hill elementary school in Albany NY. 💞 We answered questions, gave hugs, made tiktoks, delivered some @sistersapparel, made a donation, and also played Are You Smarter Than a 5th Grader? Enjoy this super cute vlog!! ☺️

node.text: Happy Sunday ☀️ I’ve always hated cheesy Instagram captions but this morning I really needed some positivity and figured that someone else out there might need some too. Friendly reminder that you are amazing, beautiful, worthy, and most importantly, you are enough. Whether you’re dealing with a tough time, tough emotions, tough people, or a tough situation, you WILL get through it. Even if it feels impossible. I promise. It might not be today, it might not be tomorrow, it might not even be soon… I know that can be really overwhelming and frightening to think about, but whenever I feel stuck, it helps me to believe that everything happens for a reason. Our battles make us smarter and stronger, and we are capable of so much more than we could ever imagine, and I really hope you know that. Love you, so so much. ❤️
